Job Description:
Brand Manager (Digital Marketing)
Responsible for the brand's overall promotion strategy, content creativity, and promotion plan planning, budget and implementation in the United States;
Responsible for the brand's official website operation (Shopify), optimizing content and user purchase experience, monitoring, analyzing and improving page views and conversion rates;
Responsible for Facebook, Instagram, Google advertising, monitoring and analysis of daily advertising data and sales. ROI analysis and optimization;
Responsible for the operation of social media such as Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, etc., Formulate, implement and optimize the fan growth plan;

